<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.9.10">
<l>cerunī ravēlvalavaṉ kalikaṉ ṟimaṅkaiyarkōṉ</l>
<l>karunīr mukilvaṇ ṇaṉkaṇṇa purattāṉai</l>
<l>yirunīriṉ tamiḻiṉ ṉicaimālai kaḷkoṇṭutoṇṭīr</l>
<l>varunīrvai yamuyya vivaipā ṭiyāṭumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Devotees, having learned [these] garlands of sweet songs</l>
<l rend="indent">in sweet Tamil of many qualities,</l>
<l>Of Kalikaṉṟi, the one skilled with a battle-quality spear,</l>
<l rend="indent">the king of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l>About the one in Kaṇṇapuram, the one the color of dark rainclouds,</l>
<l>Singing these, dance so the surging water[-clad] world will be saved.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
